    "label" : {
      "IRI-based" : "Opinion",
      "en" : "Opinion"
    },
    "comment" : {
      "en" : "A description, in the DnS sense, representing a claim held by an agent about an entity or state of affairs. An Opinion is satisfied by a Construal — the set of facts as perceived by the cognizer that grounds the claim. An Opinion is generated by a prov:Activity, which attributes it to the agent responsible for its production."
    },
