        "type" : "label"
      } ]
    },
    "label" : {
      "IRI-based" : "Construal",
      "en" : "Construal"
    },
    "comment" : {
      "en" : "A situation constituted by the premises as perceived by the agent responsible for an Opinion. It is perspective-dependent — it reifies the state of affairs from the standpoint of the cognizer, not an objective state of affairs. A Construal can be composed of parts, each of which is itself a dul:Situation representing an individual premise (i.e., another state of affairs). The dul:Situation, part of the Construal, can be satisfied by a secondary dul:Description."
    },
